videos.description: Texas' Jaxson Hayes comes up big with a colossal rejection underneath the rim.
videos.headline: Texas' Hayes get huge block under rim

videos.description: Christian James tosses up a long pass to Jamuni McNeace, who goes way up on the alley-oop to extend Oklahoma's lead over Texas.
videos.headline: McNeace goes airborne for alley-oop slam

videos.description: Freshman Jamal Bieniemy blocks a potential game-winning shot by Texas' Matt Coleman III to seal Oklahoma's 69-67 win.
videos.headline: Oklahoma freshman blocks shot to seal victory
